{"type":"message","id":"7e420eca","parentId":"d6d3217a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:54:24.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_07mtcfu6cjfb_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5251\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3072\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] experiment\r\n[mutation proposed] experiment\r\n[master 7bf29eb] pulse: 2026-03-24 105356\n 6 files changed, 356 insertions(+), 75 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 105356.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 105356.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 105258.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 105356 - CFI analysis reveals that 94.3% of frequency-invariants have CFI<0.7, meaning frequency-based compression is mostly noise/metaprogramming artifacts. The natural next step is implementing the CFI-weighted compression experiment to validate whether prioritizing causal invariants improves prediction.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"nova-basil","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5251\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3072\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] experiment\r\n[mutation proposed] experiment\r\n[master 7bf29eb] pulse: 2026-03-24 105356\n 6 files changed, 356 insertions(+), 75 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 105356.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 105356.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 105258.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 105356 - CFI analysis reveals that 94.3% of frequency-invariants have CFI<0.7, meaning frequency-based compression is mostly noise/metaprogramming artifacts. The natural next step is implementing the CFI-weighted compression experiment to validate whether prioritizing causal invariants improves prediction.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwm